Package com.google.ase.jsonrpc

Interface Summary
RpcInvoker Implementations of this interface are used to parse the JSONArray arriving from the client and invoking a particular RPC.
RpcReceiver  
 

Class Summary
JsonRpcResult Represents a JSON RPC result.
JsonRpcServer A JSON RPC server that forwards RPC calls to a specified receiver object.
RpcAnnotationHelper A helper class that helps extract descriptions and default values from parameter annotations.
RpcInfo Instances of this class describe specific RPCs on the server.
RpcInvokerFactory A factory for RpcInvoker objects.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Rpc The Rpc annotation is used to annotate server-side implementations of RPCs.
RpcDefaultBoolean This annotation marks an Integer parameter as optional and supplies a default value.
RpcDefaultInteger This annotation marks an Integer parameter as optional and supplies a default value.
RpcDefaultString This annotation marks an String parameter as optional and supplies a default value.
RpcOptionalObject This annotation marks an String parameter as optional (a value of null will be passed in if the string is not defined).
RpcOptionalString This annotation marks an String parameter as optional (a value of null will be passed in if the string is not defined).
RpcParameter An annotation that is used to document the parameters of an RPC.
